{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3ae5f8824a","title":"周恩来关于新疆红二司抄赛福鼎家等问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ea10edb31","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"3ae5f8824a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"边境地区和少数民族","id":"c0cd6cf1d4","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"81ad2a6a8d","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于新疆红二司抄赛福鼎家等问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"460e52f7e6","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：下午两点三十分〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67e2760de0","type":"paragraph","text":"周峰同志传达：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32fd80ef38","type":"paragraph","text":"总理指示说：红二司这样做是不对的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fafc157b3","type":"paragraph","text":"运动已搞了两年多了，不能再搞打、砸、抢、抄。红二司是新疆一个主要造反派，把他们放在新疆的文化大革命中的一个重要位置。他们每犯错误，（总理）都及时指出，他们自己也注意改正了，但是不能总犯错误。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"766d6605f5","type":"paragraph","text":"拿走的东西都要立即一律交还，今后不能再犯。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5d22ffbf4","type":"paragraph","text":"（抄自红二司八农兵团《九三烽火》41期68.5.8并参照红二司新大星火燎原兵团《学习参考》68.5.31所载校对）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3ae5f8824a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}